OL,3,C6.7m to cut back on showers and baths
OL,4,Cto afford rising energy bills ` survey
OL,6,FThe poll suggests 17% have not told
OL,7,Fanyone about their money worries, and
OL,8,FNational Debtline said it is concerned
OL,9,Fthat millions of people are facing
OL,10,Ffinancial struggles alone this winter.
OL,12,FOf those worried about affording their
OL,13,Fenergy bills, just 10% had spoken to
OL,14,Ftheir energy supplier and 8% had asked
OL,15,Ffor debt advice.
OL,17,FThe charity found that women are more
OL,18,Flikely than men to be concerned about
OL,19,Faffording their energy bills this
OL,20,Fwinter, but men are twice as likely to
OL,21,Fhave asked for debt advice.
