OL,3,C6.7m to cut back on showers and baths
OL,4,Cto afford rising energy bills ` survey
OL,6,FNational Debtline urged anyone worried
OL,7,Fabout their finances to contact its
OL,8,Ffree advice service.
OL,10,FIt said its advisers helped 90,000
OL,11,Fpeople deal with their debts last
OL,12,Fyear, with 80% of these seeing their
OL,13,Fdebts reduce or stabilise and 70%
OL,14,Fexperiencing a positive impact on
OL,15,Ftheir mental and emotional wellbeing.
OL,17,FNational Debtline is leading a
OL,18,Fcampaign for a Help to Repay scheme to
OL,19,Fsupport people trapped in energy debt
OL,20,Fthrough repayment matching and debt
OL,21,Fwrite-off.
