OL,6,F"It does not need to be this way ` no-
OL,7,Fone should face financial worries
OL,8,Falone this winter. I would encourage
OL,9,Fanyone worried about their finances to
OL,10,Fcontact National Debtline. Our
OL,11,Fadvisers will be able to help whatever
OL,12,Fthe situation."
OL,14,F` Opinium surveyed 2,000 UK adults
OL,15,Fbetween between November 1 and 5.
